                    </div>
                    <span>Andrea's Nonstop Networking is absolutely the best networking "How To" book written.  It sits on my desk as a reference to use the rest of my life - personally and professionally.  By changing my perspective from "What can I get from this?" to "How can I add to this?" her book takes what can seem to be a very daunting task, building lasting relationships, and breaks them into simple tasks that everyone can do everyday.  In Nonstop Networking, Andrea organizes the simple things and explains why they make all the difference.  Most importantly, her method works.  Try it.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Expert networking advice from a networking expert</div>
