                    <span>Andrea's book on nonstop networking is not only very informative, it is a very easy read with lots of real-life examples.  Of all the networking books I've read, this one is the benchmark by which all others should be measured.  Again, it is simple, straightforward, easy-to-read, full of great examples without all the extraneous words in so many books today.  Reading this book makes you want to get better at networking and do so right away.  I've recommended it to my friends and family as the one book to read on networking.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A gem for anyone who wants to be successful </div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
